title: The works of Professor Wilson of the University of Edinburgh,
author: Wilson, John
snippet: Amy rose from her seat with an air graceful as ever, but something  more matronly than that of Elliot's younger bride — and while these two fair creatures beheld each other with mutual admiration, their husbands stood there equally happy, and equally proud- George Elliot of the Priory, and Walter Harden of the Glenfoot.
